e=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705110124/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0/20200703-%E5%89%8D%E4%B9%8C%E5%9D%8E%E6%9D%91%E4%B9%A6%E8%AE%B0%E9%83%91%E9%9B%81%E9%9B%84%E4%BB%BB%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9B%BD%E5%AE%89%E5%85%AC%E7%BD%B2%E7%BD%B2%E9%95%BF |dead-url=no }}</ref>，相關言論被媒体报道后引起中國大陸境内外媒體不滿。

